text: APOEL FC () is a professional football club from Cyprus. It is based in the capital, Nicosia. == Honours == *Cyprus Chanpionship (18 in total): 1936, 1937, 1938, 1939, 1940, 1947, 1948, 1949, 1952, 1965, 1973, 1980, 1986, 1990, 1992, 1996, 2002, 2004 *Cyprus Cup (17 in total): in 1937, 1941, 1947, 1951, 1963, 1968, 1969, 1973, 1976, 1978, 1979, 1984, 1993, 1995, 1996, 1997, 1999. == Other websites == * Official website of APOEL FC * Official website of APOEL fans Category:Cypriot football clubs Category:Nicosia
